<emphasis id="B90C8B30984F7053C5CDFA8FFB02FAF7" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="29">Thallus saxicolus, parvus. Laciniae filiformes, subteretiusculae. Pseudocyphellae lineares. Soralia lateralia vel laminalia. Pycnidia non visa. Apothecia nulla. Acida usnicum, sekikaicum, hypoprotocetraricum et succinprotocetraricum continens.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
